{"tid":478571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將674中國翻牆app下架 Apple：留低才能推動言論自由","createTime":"2017-11-24T07:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T12:51:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c149a0abf03f888d032a70818afde7ef6eed17a8","tid":478571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171124/20224379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F20224379&d=mFMdzWpOsUGUWZ56RlTWqnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5135abc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171124%2F20224379&h=905a73d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171124/20224379</a><br />\n<br />\n將674中國翻牆app下架<br />\nApple：留低才能推動言論自由<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞  <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國蘋果公司於當地時間21日承認，應中國政府要求，今年已下架中國區應用商店（App Store）內的674個VPN應用程式。蘋果解釋，這樣做使公司得以繼續留在中國，從而推動言論自由等基本權益。<br />\n<br />\n今年10月，美國參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）和萊希（Patrick Leahy）聯名致函蘋果公司行政總裁庫克，質疑蘋果公司下架VPN的決定。蘋果公司作出相關回應。該兩名美國參議員說，防火長城對中國人民的威脅，不亞於柏林圍牆對東德人民的威脅。只要防火長城在，並獲得美國技術公司的支持，中國的互聯網自由就仍處於風險中。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司在回信中提到，該公司在中國的存在「有助於促進更大程度的開放，推動思想和信息的自由流動」。蘋果公司公共政策副總裁Cynthia Hogan辯稱：「我們深信，讓蘋果公司能最好地推動基本權益， 包括言論自由權的方式就是參與，儘管我們可能不同意某些國家的法律。」蘋果公司表示，曾質詢過中國當局要求下架VPN的法律依據。當局回覆，這些軟件違反中國法律，包括《網絡安全法》第27條等。<br />\n<br />\nVPN稱為虛擬私人網絡，可以改變並加密用戶的互聯網接入地址。在防火長城高聳的中國，網民們用此來繞開互聯網封鎖，即所謂的「翻牆」。<br />\n<br />\nThe Register"},{"pid":"930709b1da59bcd31a4a17b6c101b382ed11e632","tid":478571,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"456fa9d0a02b1a06b4a2e649ad468c12143a9c29","tid":478571,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"Apple唔係傻到以為佢有能力係中國推動言論自由呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04fdddba67dbbdfa7816ba404fb2315e424e632","tid":478571,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"android 無store都可以自己裝app<br />\nIOS 而家又JB唔到，真係無得裝"},{"pid":"59947f6f1ded96ae464d75df6e9353e40885f24a","tid":478571,"uid":57705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11f96c55513683eca41c220daa09d794b7b9b11a","tid":478571,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Apple唔係傻到以為佢有能力係中國推動言論自由呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係傻到以為Apple想係中國推動言論自由呀?</blockquote><br />\napple 內置微博就知咩事啦嘛"},{"pid":"246420ac17961937946d74cd45232db1c361b59b","tid":478571,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa36dc1ee98cca409d71ace4a9f4ec01ffaee780","tid":478571,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple唔係傻到以為佢有能力係中國推動言論自由呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講錢啫<br />\n洗理佢點狡辯咩"},{"pid":"b9cc15444fb6ae47f6b41b956c1e4cad373fb57d","tid":478571,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Apple唔係傻到以為佢有能力係中國推動言論自由呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係傻到以為Apple想係中國推動言論自由呀?</blockquote><br />\napple 內置微博就知咩事啦嘛</blockquote><br />\n一開機default開晒有一半都係支那社交媒體<br />\n以為自己買咗華為呀"},{"pid":"ea0e4e5c41a46f511449aa533f83708863563eb5","tid":478571,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201